Sorry for the delay. Another crazy drama filled day. From POV - alex/Amanda actually staying this week - Allison & Sheila getting into a huge fight - Amanda passing out - Allison almost dying - Sheila going nuts - etc... - etc... I&#039;m going to make this quick.

Part 1 - 19 min
Right after POV. Josh/Sharon won and they all talk about what their going to do this week.

Part 2 - 15 min
Sheila&#039;s blood pressure is rising and she&#039;s getting pissed.

Part 3 - 17 min
More of the group meeting in the HOH and then Sheila is discussed.

Part 4 - 10 min
Sheila and now Natalie are pissed at Allison and they tell the group.

Part 5 - 10 min
Josh, the little gossip, tells Allison everything that Sheila said downstairs. He just loves to stir up shit.

Part 6 - 24 min
Allison and Sheila get into a HUGE fight - Then they make up.

Part 7 - 1 min
Amanda passes out. One of the craziest moments in BB history.

Part 8 - 10 min
Reaction after the feeds came back on. We learn that Allison went to the hospital too because of some allergic reaction.

Part 9 - 9 min
Sharon/Josh talk about what to do this week. They want to make a deal with Alex/Amanda and take out Nat/Matt this week.

Part 10 - 12 min
Amanda comes back into the house - Nat is sick and Sheila won&#039;t leave her alone because she has to bitch about Adam.

Part 11 - 20 min
Allison comes back into the house - Sheila/Amanda/Allison have a heart to heart.

Part 12 - 10 min
All 3 girls battle for attention - Sheila now says Adam sexually harasses her and she wants the DR to sit him down and give him a little talking to.

Part 13 - 10 min
Sheila & Adam have a talk. He just sits there and agrees with her so she will STFU.
